      "abstract": [
        {
          "contentType": "purpose",
          "lang": "fr",
          "value": "Le but de cette étude était d'évaluer l'information reçues par les femmes enceintes au sujet des expositions possibles à cinq agents reprotoxiques au cours de leur grossesse."
        },
        {
          "contentType": "purpose",
          "lang": "en",
          "value": "The aim of this study was to assess the information received by pregnant women about possible exposure to five reprotoxic agents during pregnancy."
